<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">م ل ص:</span> <span class="c2">(الْمَلَصُ)</span> بِفَتْحَتَيْنِ الزَّلَقُ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(مَلِصَ)</span> الشَّيْءُ مِنْ يَدِي مِنْ بَابِ طَرِبَ وَ <span class="c2">(انْمَلَصَ)</span> الشَّيْءُ: أَفْلَتَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>